<SECOND>BC-Auto Sales,0247</SECOND>
<HEAD>Ford, Chrysler Daily Car Sales Rise</HEAD>
<NOTE>Eds: An AMer expected by 6:30 p.m. EDT</NOTE>
<DATELINE>DETROIT (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
